{"tid":734722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"風雨見人心！日本600國高中生 前進重災區清理","createTime":"2018-07-09T01:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T12:02:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4c5fcd4d9fd7252ef7dee4bad2d4d0b4a25e416a","tid":734722,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"日本豪雨在多地造成嚴重災情，傳出已有68人喪命，死傷人數最多的分別是廣島縣29人、愛媛縣20人、岡山縣8人。其中岡山倉敷市真備町更有上千人受困屋頂待援，岡山總社市國高中生們則發揮人溺己溺的精神，在網路號召的力量下，聚集600人志願清理災區。<br />\n<br />\n據《NHK》報導，總社市當地各國中與高中的學生，透過社交平台的聯繫，今（8日）上午共有600人在總社市政府集結，進行支援受災民眾的行動。<br />\n<br />\n有9名學生在日羽地區協助居民鏟除淤泥，69歲的老者感激地說，自己的腰部很不好，屋況那麼糟糕真不知該怎麼收拾，真的很感謝來幫忙的年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n1名參加救助災民活動的高2學生透露，真正來到災區時，才發現受損狀況想像中還嚴重。總社高中1年級學生則說，他覺得自己可以幫災民做些什麼，所以就來了，到了集合地點後讓他非常驚訝，因為他沒想過會有那麼多人來幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2481948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2481948&d=EhObDzPWrntWObDqJW3iFIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a0735767\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2481948&h=b5cbac8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2481948</a>"},{"pid":"4618660e891c935a0589c57ec3af16c3f5210509","tid":734722,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"日本雨災增至88人死亡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本西部廣泛地區受暴雨侵襲，引發泥石流及山泥傾瀉，遇難人數陸續增至88人，至少58人下落不明，另有4名傷者情況危殆。在廣島，有20幢建築物被泥石流覆蓋，造成38人死亡，愛媛縣有21人喪生，岡山則有10人。今次是近20年來，日本遭受最大一次洪澇災害，當地傳媒推測，最終死亡人數有可能接近200人。當局指，多個縣極可能發生地質災害，包括愛媛、德島、廣島、山口及滋賀縣；出動54000多名救援人員及40多架直升機救災。<br />\n<br />\n廣島、愛媛及岡山近3000幢房屋損壞， 在人口有2.2萬人的岡山縣倉敷市真備町，有河流決堤，導致3成地區被淹浸。全縣有過千人被困醫院及建築物頂層，等待當局派出直升機及船艇將他們救出。氣象廳一度向岐阜、愛媛及高知縣發出大雨特別警報，指示或建議19個府縣260萬戶家庭、總計590萬人疏散，目前20個府縣有3萬多人到避難所暫避。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1018107&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1018107%26csid%3D261_367&d=EhObDzPWrntWObDqJW3iFIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8de4f904\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1018107&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"ea4d92a4ff27eb4f9ef19acbb05a738e10429f65","tid":734722,"uid":191815,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:49:32.000Z","msg":"月尾會去四国同中国，到時如果有募金活動應該都會參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ea4e0013494d4e94f9043266bee34359bf2f7a","tid":734722,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6700cb409f1334e8f4e56acfa605913e75a072","tid":734722,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:17:56.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2200a2d8bf08e9b6e0b7200442afc2780daa00a7","tid":734722,"uid":174191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"天佑日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb197e5be5fe446c32af9e6ccfab63f4a4f82f60","tid":734722,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2200a2d8bf08e9b6e0b7200442afc2780daa00a7","tid":734722,"uid":174191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"天佑日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:37:39.000Z","msg":"希望下次發生係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就講中國人民來扛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\"